  "prompt": "Which is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Upson County GA?",
  "response": "A suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Upson County, GA, is the \"Pine Lodge Treatment Center\" located in nearby Pine Mountain, GA. Here are some key details about the facility:\n\n- **Address**: 100 Pine Lodge Rd, Pine Mountain, GA 31822\n- **Phone**: (706) 663-0111\n- **Services**: Pine Lodge offers comprehensive inpatient treatment programs for substance abuse and co-occurring mental health disorders. Their services include detox, residential treatment, individual and group therapy, family therapy, and aftercare planning.\n- **Accreditation**: The center is accredited by The Joint Commission, ensuring high standards of care.\n- **Distance from Upson County**: Approximately 30 miles, which is about a 40-minute drive.\n\nIt's always a good idea to call the facility directly to discuss your specific needs and to verify current availability and any admission requirements. Additionally, checking with your insurance provider to see if they cover treatment at Pine Lodge can be helpful.",
